@node Main "68000 Execution Times"
From Motorola's:
--------------------------------------------------------------
M68000 8-/16-/32-BIT MICROPROCESSORS USER'S MANUAL (Section 8) 
--------------------------------------------------------------
Retyped by Subhuman/Epsilon
Converted to Amiga Guide by Dancing Fool/Epsilon

