|  CHK (No Trap) |     -     |    10+   |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  EORI to CCR   |   Byte    |    20    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  EORI to SR    |   Word    |    20    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  ORI to CCR    |   Byte    |    20    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  ORI to SR     |   Word    |    20    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  MOVE from SR  |     -     |    6     |   8+   |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  MOVE to CCR   |     -     |    12    |   12+  |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  MOVE to SR    |     -     |    6     |   12+  |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  EXG           |     -     |    6     |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|                |   Word    |    4     |   -    |
|  EXT           +-----------+----------+--------+
|                |   Long    |    4     |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  LINK          |     -     |    16    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  MOVE from USP |     -     |    4     |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  MOVE to USP   |     -     |    4     |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  NOP           |     -     |    4     |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  RESET         |     -     |   132    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  RTE           |     -     |    20    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  RTR           |     -     |    20    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  RTS           |     -     |    16    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  STOP          |     -     |    4     |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  SWAP          |     -     |    4     |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  TRAPV         |     -     |    4     |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
|  UNLK          |     -     |    12    |   -    |
+----------------+-----------+----------+--------+
